1
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:07,500
♪That dangerous temptation♪

2
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,020
♪Like a whirlpool churning deep♪

3
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:12,900
♪Like a moth darts into the flame♪

4
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:14,340
♪Falling towards the light♪

5
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:17,420
♪Watch as everything drowns in shadows♪

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,340
♪Have no fear, do not retreat♪

7
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:23,220
♪See the blazing sparks ignite♪

8
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:27,060
♪Believe this all has cause and effect♪

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,460
♪No evil escapes untouched♪

10
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,820
♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

11
00:00:32,060 --> 00:00:34,850
♪The memories howl as they flash by♪

12
00:00:34,850 --> 00:00:37,820
[Miss Mystery]

13
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:40,160
Xin.

14
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,400
Ms. Lin, you called me here so late.

15
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:51,360
What do you want me
to investigate this time?

16
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,760
The orphanage.

17
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:54,640
The orphanage?

18
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:57,040
Isn't it the Zhu family's property?

19
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:59,120
[Lianhe Orphanage]
Why do you need me to look into it?

20
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,520
Except for the orphanage,
I need you to look into someone.

21
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:02,960
Who is that?

22
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,760
Zhu Mao.

23
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:07,680
Zhu Mao? Mr. Zhu Jr.'s father?

24
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,440
Yes.

25
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:11,020
I know that Zhu Mao
is using the orphanage

26
00:01:11,020 --> 00:01:12,440
for some illegal dealings,

27
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:15,320
but I need more specifics from you
to further investigate.

28
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,160
Looks like Mr. Zhu Jr.
doesn't know this thing.

29
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,920
I hope you can
keep this confidential for me this time.

30
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:26,560
My lips are sealed.
Your secrets are safe with me.

31
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:43,340
[Episode 17]

32
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:56,920
Enjoy.

33
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,160
Mr. Lin,

34
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,720
thank you for helping her this time.

35
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:04,200
Also, thank you for
taking care of Bao'er all these years.

36
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,480
Mr. Zhu Jr., your words
sound a bit strange.

37
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:09,760
I don't need an outsider
to thank me for helping Bao'er.

38
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,520
Meeting me privately here,

39
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,360
you must have something to say to me.

40
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,440
As expected, you are a smart man.

41
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,840
You want to take Bao'er away
with you this time, right?

42
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,960
Since you already know that,

43
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,560
why would you ask me here?

44
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,760
Because you can be at ease

45
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,720
after seeing me.

46
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,440
How confident, Mr. Zhu Jr.

47
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,560
I'm willing to sacrifice everything

48
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:38,920
to protect her

49
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,640
and love her.

50
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,960
You are her most important family,

51
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:47,200
so I make sure you know my promise.

52
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,440
On Lianhe Town's turf,

53
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,320
no one is more powerful
than the Zhu family.

54
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:55,080
Your assurance
does not hold much sincerity.

55
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,640
Between the Zhu family

56
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,400
and Bao'er,

57
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,320
if I have to make a choice,

58
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,520
I will always choose Bao'er.

59
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,080
Bao'er means the world to me.

60
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:24,260
[BABY RESTAURANT]

61
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,120
You're here so early.

62
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,000
Mr. Lin just came to Lianhe Town

63
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,320
and is new in town.

64
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,240
So I picked him up from the hotel.

65
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,760
Are you trying to curry favor
with my brother behind my back?

66
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:43,240
What's wrong with being friendly
with my brother-in-law?

67
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,800
I'm sorry.

68
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,120
I want to spend more time
with my brother today.

69
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,920
So I'll neglect you a bit.

70
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,520
Alright.

71
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,680
Caesar salad,

72
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,560
filet steak, and tomato pasta.

73
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,160
My in-law,

74
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,840
do you want anything else?

75
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:06,640
A

76
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,520
thick toast.

77
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,560
I know you so well.

78
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,920
You loved eating that
since you were a child.

79
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,080
Sweet tooth.

80
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,000
Looks like

81
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,320
you know very well what Bao'er likes.

82
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,280
Certainly,

83
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:22,920
she's my sister, after all.

84
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:28,880
Yes, closer than your birth sister.

85
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,480
As her husband,

86
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,600
don't you know anything
about Bao'er's preferences?

87
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,720
Of course, I do.

88
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:38,080
What I ordered are her favorites.

89
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,880
I even bought the restaurant...

90
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,400
Bao'er, try this.

91
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,600
Bao'er likes eating vegetables first.

92
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,200
Yes.

93
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,280
That's healthy.

94
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,480
Jiacheng, you are still acting like
when we were little,

95
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,920
making me eat vegetables first.

96
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,680
Dig in.

97
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,520
Mr. Lin, you rarely come to Lianhe Town.

98
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:23,440
My wife and I
will do a good job as hosts.

99
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:24,520
After this meal,

100
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,680
let us show you around.

101
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:27,760
No, don't bother.

102
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,280
After visiting Bao'er,

103
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,600
I'm going back to Southeast Asia.

104
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,880
So early?

105
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:34,880
Mr. Zhu Jr.,

106
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:37,840
I'm handing my sister to you.

107
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:40,080
I'm always available
if you need any help.

108
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,520
However, if Bao'er is harmed in any way,

109
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,720
I will hold you accountable first.

110
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,660
[BABY RESTAURANT]

111
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,800
Alright,

112
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,760
I'll go get my car.

113
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,040
Thanks.

114
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,240
Bao'er,

115
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,920
have you found any clues
about what you're looking for?

116
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,480
Not yet.

117
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:24,600
But I'm very sure
that it's in the Zhu manor.

118
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,920
I think Zhu Guanwen sincerely loves you.

119
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,680
When do you plan to tell him?

120
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,760
I haven't decided yet.

121
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,400
But I have no choice.

122
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:40,120
In my opinion, he knows everything,

123
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,040
but he is willingly being used by you.

124
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:49,580
[Dou Manor]

125
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,000
Lili,

126
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:02,000
look at you,
throwing a tantrum every day,

127
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,760
making everyone gloomy.

128
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:09,240
Dad, how can you take in such shame?

129
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,080
Of course, I can't.

130
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:15,880
But Lianhe Town nowadays
is out of order.

131
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,960
We must not lose our composure.

132
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,400
Dad,

133
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,280
what do you plan to do?

134
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,160
Without taking care of Lin Bao'er,

135
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,360
we will give away the shipping company
sooner or later.

136
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,560
Don't you think I know?

137
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,540
Our enemies

138
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:47,320
are not just Lin Bao'er alone.

139
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:50,600
We need to consider this
from a long-term perspective.

140
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,120
Do you mean

141
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:55,760
the Zhu family?

142
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:04,600
If we take control

143
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,200
of Lianhe Town in the future,

144
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,920
won't you have anything you want?

145
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,840
Actually, I don't want him
to leave Lianhe Town.

146
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,120
Why? Does he want you to be his wife?

147
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:33,880
Guanwen,

148
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:37,760
I've told you, he's my closest family.

149
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,440
Yes.

150
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,320
He'd better be.

151
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:45,400
Also, for me to come back here,

152
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,200
he supported me greatly.

153
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,880
You are quite lucky, actually,

154
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,840
to have such a close family.

155
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,600
Not like me.

156
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,960
Guanwen...

157
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,840
Don't worry.

158
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,160
I have you now,

159
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:04,880
and I'm content.

160
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,760
Then,

161
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,960
if you find out I hurt you one day,

162
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:13,840
what will you do?

163
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,160
If you hurt me one day,

164
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,760
then I will hate you
for the rest of my life,

165
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,480
unless you buy me candies.

166
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,720
Alright, stop thinking about that.

167
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,640
Have a candy, and it will cheer you up.

168
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,000
I'm not a child.

169
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,120
What? You don't like it?

170
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,640
I didn't expect

171
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:47,040
that my wife would
have such a childish side.

172
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,960
Why did you do that?

173
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:16,020
♪The end has now been reached♪

174
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:18,940
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

175
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:22,260
♪Looking away from you♪

176
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:26,380
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

177
00:10:26,540 --> 00:10:29,860
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

178
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:34,860
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

179
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:41,460
♪In a moment♪

180
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:44,340
♪Flitting images flashing♪

181
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:46,740
♪Eyes fall shut♪

182
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:50,540
♪Fingertips gently touched♪

183
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:53,980
♪Risking fate and danger venturing♪

184
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:55,860
♪Dancing on the tip of the knife♪

185
00:10:55,980 --> 00:11:02,140
♪Put on a show wholeheartedly♪

186
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:06,300
♪In a moment♪

187
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:09,220
♪The memory in my mind♪

188
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:11,140
♪Surging at me♪

189
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:15,500
♪Beliefs hidden deep inside♪

190
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:18,580
♪In an abyss perhaps inescapable♪

191
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:21,780
♪Under a ray of light in the darkness♪

192
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:24,820
♪I may reopen my eyes♪
